{"markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"","page-layout":"full","toc":false},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<section style=\"padding: 4rem 0 2rem;\">\n  <div class=\"section-label\">Get in touch</div>\n  <h1>Contact</h1>\n  <hr class=\"neon-rule\">\n</section>\n```\n\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; padding-bottom: 5rem; align-items: start;\">\n\n  <div>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1.05rem; color:#e2e2e2; line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 2rem;\">\n      I'm always open to conversations about data, analytics, projects,\n      or opportunities. Whether you're a recruiter, a potential collaborator,\n      or a fellow student, feel free to reach out.\n    </p>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;\">\n\n      <a href=\"mailto:raunit.budhiraja@mail.dcu.ie\" class=\"project-card\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n        <div class=\"card-tag\">Email</div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-size: 0.95rem;\">raunit.budhiraja@mail.dcu.ie</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:0.85rem;\">Fastest way to reach me. I typically reply within 24 hours.</p>\n      </a>\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/raunit-budhiraja-980595203/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"project-card\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n        <div class=\"card-tag\">LinkedIn</div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-size: 0.95rem;\">linkedin.com/in/raunitbudhiraja</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:0.85rem;\">Connect professionally — I'm open to networking in analytics and tech.</p>\n      </a>\n\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/raunitbudhiraja02\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"project-card\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n        <div class=\"card-tag\">GitHub</div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-size: 0.95rem;\">github.com/raunitbudhiraja</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:0.85rem;\">Where all the code for this portfolio and other projects lives.</p>\n      </a>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div>\n    <div style=\"background: #14141f; border: 1px solid #252535; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\">Currently</div>\n\n      <div class=\"timeline\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n          <div class=\"tl-date\">2025 – Present</div>\n          <h3>Final Year, BSc Business Analytics</h3>\n          <p>Dublin City University</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n          <div class=\"tl-date\">Looking for</div>\n          <h3>Summer Internship / Graduate Role</h3>\n          <p>Data analyst, business analyst, or junior data science roles in Ireland or remote.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n          <div class=\"tl-date\">Interests</div>\n          <h3>Python · ML · BI · Strategy</h3>\n          <p>Especially interested in companies where analytics sits close to product decisions.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 1.5rem;\">\n        <a href=\"cv/raunit_cv.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn-neon\" style=\"width:100%; justify-content:center;\">\n          Download CV (PDF) →\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<section style=\"padding: 4rem 0 2rem;\">\n  <div class=\"section-label\">Get in touch</div>\n  <h1>Contact</h1>\n  <hr class=\"neon-rule\">\n</section>\n```\n\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; padding-bottom: 5rem; align-items: start;\">\n\n  <div>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1.05rem; color:#e2e2e2; line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 2rem;\">\n      I'm always open to conversations about data, analytics, projects,\n      or opportunities. Whether you're a recruiter, a potential collaborator,\n      or a fellow student, feel free to reach out.\n    </p>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;\">\n\n      <a href=\"mailto:raunit.budhiraja@mail.dcu.ie\" class=\"project-card\" style=\"text-deco